.. actex:: herd
   :author: Leon Kim
   :difficulty: 0.0
   :basecourse: thinkcspy
   :topic: PythonTurtle/Exercises
   :from_source: F

   Write a program with the following requirements:

   a. Write a program that will create four (4) turtles with the names of 4 students in this class.
   b. Change their colors and pen size.
   c. Change your turtles to a different shape. Each turtle will have a different shape.
   d. Have your turtles create a cool design with multiple colors and shapes on your canvas.
   e. Use at least one new function from the API that you have not yet used. Besides "shape".

   ~~~~